[CovertActionNarrative_CommanderSupplyInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Neutralize Logistics Officer"
ActionPreNarrative="Resistance operatives have identified a high-level target. This commander is in charge of <font color='#CBB11F'>logistics</font> for the entire region, and we know where he is."
ActionPostNarrative="Tygan has cracked the officer's neural implant and recovered fragmentary details of a vulnerable supply line. We have work to do."

[CovertActionNarrative_SupplyRaidInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Secure ADVENT Materials"
ActionPreNarrative="This location is host to an ADVENT <font color='#CBB11F'>supply convoy</font>. Unlike the thousands of other such convoys, this one is isolated and ready for the taking. It will be a heavily defended target nonetheless."
ActionPostNarrative="A job well done, Commander. I trust you will put your spoils of war to good use."

[CovertActionNarrative_RecoverInformantInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Recover VIP Schedule"
ActionPreNarrative="The Resistance has learned of a civilian ADVENT collaborator operating in this region. They should have a <font color='#27AAE1'>wealth of intel</font> on ADVENT's operations. We can bring them in for questioning, but first they need to be found."
ActionPostNarrative="The collaborator's whereabouts have been safely recovered. Let's go pay them a visit."

[CovertActionNarrative_CaptureInformantInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Capture ADVENT Collaborator"
ActionPreNarrative="Unlike ADVENT officers, civilian traitors will <font color='#27AAE1'>reveal what they know</font> under 'questioning'. We know where the target will be in a few days - it's time for a kidnap job."
ActionPostNarrative="I'm glad to see the operation was a success, Commander. Our mutual friend is being questioned as we speak."

[CovertActionNarrative_PrepareCounterDE X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Identify Critical Project Data"
ActionPreNarrative="We know the aliens are working on their <font color='#E52E11'><XGParam:StrValue4/></font> project, and there must be a vulnerability somewhere. All we need to do is find it."
ActionPostNarrative="Our operatives managed to get a fix on the location of a vulnerability in the ADVENT network. If we strike now, we may be able to stop the <font color='#E52E11'><XGParam:StrValue4/></font>."

[CovertActionNarrative_CounterDarkEventInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Eliminate Critical Datalink"
ActionPreNarrative="We've found a weakspot in the aliens' plans to implement their <font color='#E52E11'><XGParam:StrValue4/></font> project. If we collapse this data relay, we can stop their progress."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_RecoverPersonnelInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Breach ADVENT Arrest Database"
ActionPreNarrative="Word from our informants is that ADVENT's put a dent into the <font color='#33AB13'>academic community</font> in this region. If we hit this data vault, we can find out where they went."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_RescueScientistInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Rescue Scientist"
ActionPreNarrative="The breach of the data vault has revealed that one of ADVENT's recent arrests posesses <font color='#33AB13'>high scientific knowledge</font> and is currently underdefended. It would be foolish to refuse this invitation."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_RescueEngineerInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Rescue Engineer"
ActionPreNarrative="Our newfound access to the ADVENT database shows that a recent detainee has extensive <font color='#33AB13'>experience in the technical arts</font>. Not to mention they're sitting in a blindspot of ADVENT's security grid. Let's go get 'em."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_PrepareFactionJB X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Consult the Faction"
ActionPreNarrative="We could use additional field support from the <FactionName>. If we send a delegation, they may be willing to commit another soldier to XCOM's ranks."
ActionPostNarrative="Good news, the <FactionName> has agreed with our proposal. Bad news, the soldier pledged to our cause has recently been captured. If we want their support, we'll have to stage a jailbreak."

[CovertActionNarrative_JailbreakSoldierInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Rescue Captured Soldier"
ActionPreNarrative="One of our soldiers, <SolderName>, was captured by the enemy recently, and we know where they're being held. It's time for a jailbreak."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_JailbreakChosenSoldierInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Rescue Captured Soldier"
ActionPreNarrative="One of our soldiers, <SolderName>, was captured by the Chosen recently, and we know where they're being held. It's time for a jailbreak."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_JailbreakFactionSoldierInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Rescue Captured Faction Soldier"
ActionPreNarrative="The factions have reported to us that one of their most skilled operatives was ambushed and taken captive recently. We'll be generously rewarded should we break them out."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_RecoverUFOInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Recover UFO Command Codes"
ActionPreNarrative="That damned UFO has been a thorn in our sides for too long. Resistance operatives have identified an opportunity to steal a copy of their command codes, and <font color='#CBB11F'>force it to ground</font>."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_PrepareUFO X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Force the UFO to Ground"
ActionPreNarrative="With the command codes in hand, we can trick the UFO into <font color='#CBB11F'>setting down</font>. Then we must set up a jamming net to delay its calls for help once the main assault squad goes in. We won't get another chance at this."
ActionPostNarrative="Commander, we've achieved stunning success! The alien ship has touched down, and the jamming net is in place. I think they're starting to get wise, though, so we should strike immediately."

[CovertActionNarrative_PrepareFacility X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Identify Avatar Project Collaborators"
ActionPreNarrative="The aliens have buried the construction of <font color='#842015'>Avatar facilities</font> fairly deep, but there must be at least one human in the know. At least one weak link. We just have to find it."
ActionPostNarrative="Commander, after 'borrowing' some ADVENT records, my team found one human higher-up who was involved in the construction of an <font color='#842015'>Avatar facility</font>. Even better, we know where they are."

[CovertActionNarrative_FacilityInformantInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Capture Avatar Collaborator"
ActionPreNarrative="Our friends in the Resistance have found someone who may know where the <font color='#842015'>hidden facility</font> is. All that's left is the hard part - bringing them in for questioning."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_IntelRescueInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Save Intercepted Courier"
ActionPreNarrative="On the way back to a Resistance Haven, one of our <font color='#27AAE1'>couriers carrying intel</font> from the last mission was attacked and narrowly escaped, but is now trapped. ADVENT forces will find the courier's foxhole any day now, unless we intervene."
ActionPostNarrative=""

[CovertActionNarrative_SupplyRescueInfil X2CovertActionNarrativeTemplate]
ActionName="Save Intercepted Convoy"
ActionPreNarrative="On the way back to a nearby Resistance Haven, one of our <font color='#CBB11F'>supply convoys</font> from the last mission was interdicted by ADVENT troops. They escaped, but had to detour through a Lost city. If we don't send help, the convoy isn't coming home."
ActionPostNarrative=""

